 820, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"paintings\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"naked athletes\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"weapons\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The interpretation of the Greek God Dionysus makes us aware of the absurdity of violence between human beings.#Paris2024#OpeningCeremonypic.twitter.com/FBlQNNUmvV He continued: \\\"So there I came, simply, to sing this song.\\\"\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9933546761098778, \"rank\": 0.003098252841649403, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.570030524617596e-16, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The interpretation\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"the absurdity\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"human beings.#Paris2024#OpeningCeremonypic.twitter.com/FBlQNNUmvV\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"this song\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED :2024 Paris Olympics Organizers Apologize For 'Offensive' Opening Ceremony, Largest Sponsor Pulls Advertising For 'Unacceptable Mockery' Katerine, a songwriter, said he was \\\"deeply sorry\\\" if his appearance offended any of the millions of viewers and that his intention was a \\\"misunderstanding.\\\"\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2024 Paris Olympics Organizers\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"'Offensive' Opening Ceremony\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"Sponsor\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"'Unacceptable Mockery' Katerine\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"a songwriter\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"his appearance\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"the millions\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1501}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"his intention\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"misunderstanding\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was brought up as a Christian and the best thing about Christianity is forgiveness,\\\" he told 'CNN.'\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9441134455996087, \"rank\": 0.05916593736664206, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9466740785882145, \"rank\": 0.05632862513374173, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.4801888396721913e-11, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best thing\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 161